title: Mind The Reentry
description:
This week Jessica and June are coming in HOT but they’re cooling off at reentry. Jessica updates us on her east coast trip which includes walking angrily in the rain and consorting with locals to find out where the Martha Stewart gets her Lobsters. And June lets us know that she off-line for six days and learned to read again, and yes, her Pickleball Summer is continuing. Deep Divers remember, we’re all in various forms of reentry, please be safe out there.

 

More info for Plan C pills https://www.plancpills.org/

Visit the Pinterest Board pinterest.com/thedeepdive 

You can follow The Deep Dive on Twitter @thedeepdivepod
